snippet.title: NewRetroWave
snippet.description:
NewRetroWave is a network dedicated to promoting the BEST in the growing Synthwave scene. Since it's EST. in Nov 2011, NewRetroWave has grown and evolved into a prominent musical hub and online presence where the Synthwave scene is given its due exposure. You are all about to embark on a journey into new retro sounds that will change your lives forever!

We upload weekly on Mon - Friday.

If you want your music or artwork removed from our Youtube Channel/ website, please email our legal team at:   legal@newretrowave.com


We host - Synthwave/ Retrowave/ Dreamwave/ Darksynth/ EBM/ Cyberpunk/ Retro-Electro/ Chillwave/ VaporTrap/ Synthpop/ Synthfunk.
